这样，UART就被初始化好了，可以用来与外围设备进行通信。如果你使用的是旧版的标准外设库，那么可能会用到 USART_Init() 函数，但在现代STM32开发中，HAL库是更推荐的选择。

When you try to bind the same type as a singleton in more than one binding, Zenject detects the duplicate singleton registration and throws a ZenjectException. This exception is triggered during the binding process with a message indicating that the type has already been bound as a singleton (via AsSingle) and can’t be bound again in that manner.

In other words, if you have:

  Container.Bind<MyType>().AsSingle();
  Container.Bind<MyType>().AsSingle();

Zenject will throw a ZenjectException with an error message explaining the conflict.

This behavior is intentional so that you don’t accidentally register multiple bindings that claim “singleton” status for the same type.

